gomodel:SYNGO_2026  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Fig. 2: \"In the presence of 100 nM α-CTx-MII, a concentration that has been shown to selectively and maximally inhibit α3β2* nAChR (Cartier et al., 1996; Kaiser et al., 1998), [3H]dopamine release evoked by 10 μM nicotine was decreased by 35.5 ± 4.9% (n = 3,p < 0.01; Fig. 2).\". Experimental description: \"[3H]Dopamine release from rat striatal synaptosomes was measured as described previously (Kaiser et al., 1998). In brief, male Sprague-Dawley rats (250-350 g) ...\"" ;
